‘Never in a million years did I think I would be getting married without my mother there. Planning for my wedding was actually one of the last things my mom and I did together before she was killed,’ Ms Lafferty told the magazine.

Ms Lafferty and longtime fiance Christopher Smegielski were married at Ms Hochsprung’s upstate New York lake house in the Adirondacks.

